column1: Bosscat Kitchen & Libations////This a nice place to eat and the vibes are good. My friend and I recently visited and we were pleased. We ordered the tater tots with chorizo
column4: and a poached egg. I forgot what that particular dish was called but it was great. We both got full off of it
column5: so the portion sizes are great! You definitely get what you pay for. Will be returning.
